			This section is for technical writing, project updates, derivations, reading notes, and
			short explanations that are useful enough to keep.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="empty-state">
			<p class="eyebrow">draft queue</p>
			<h2>First posts are still being assembled.</h2>
			<p>
				Likely topics include quantum dot modeling, simulation habits, photonics references,
				and notes from engineering physics coursework or lab work.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
